  "texts": [
    "First, we use the feature-extracted vectors as input to train the autoencoder component.",
    "The objective of the autoencoder is to minimize the error between the input and its reconstruction, thereby learning a compact representation of the data.",
    "In this stage, the autoencoder's weight parameters are updated using backpropagation.",
    "After training, we extract the output from the encoder, which represents the latent feature vectors.",
    "These vectors serve as the new representation of the data features."
